```
# Rust-specific ignores
target/
Cargo.lock

# Dependencies
vendor/

# Compiled and build artifacts
**/*.rs.bk
**/*.rlib
**/*.so
**/*.dylib
**/*.dll
**/*.a
**/*.lib

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*

# OS specific
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Cache directories
**/__pycache__/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
```